

     
      People Who Should Be Phased Out...  * People who always harmonize the last few notes of "Happy Birthday."  * People over 40 who can't put on reading glasses without making self-conscious remarks about their advancing age.  * People who wink when they're kidding.  * Men who propose marriage on the giant TV screen at a sports stadium.  * A celebrity couple who adopt a Third-World baby and call it Rain Forest.  * People who have memorised a lot of TV-show theme songs and are really proud of it.  * Women who think it's really cute to have first names consisting solely of initials or three names.  * People who give their house or car a name.  * People who can juggle, but only a little bit.  * Actors who drive race cars.  * People who wear watches on the inside of their wrists. 
     
    
